<p>The headline numbers are striking. On DreamX's own 5-second evaluation, the 5B DreamX model leads the 8B HY-WorldPlay 1.5 and the 14B/28B LingBot-World on overall score and camera control. The same pattern holds at ~30 seconds and on revisit-consistency metrics. But the benchmark is internally designed and aligned with Omni-WorldBench/WorldScore axes, not an official public leaderboard, so the absolute numbers should be read as a relative signal among these three systems rather than as a universal ranking.</p>

